title: CocoLuscious Factory Shop
description: A factory direct shop offering vegan coconut milk ice cream in sixteen flavors: chocolate, vanilla, coconut, raspberry, blueberry, mango, chai, vanilla choc chip, peppermint choc chip, coffee, chilli chocolate, choc chip cookie dough, vanilla gold, chocolate gold, vanilla Christmas, and chocolate Christmas. Phone before you visit so that they can have your items ready.
streetAddress: 7-9 Ern Harley Drive, 2H Burleigh Gardens Commercial Centre, Burleigh Heads
